title: New mobile element found in mosquito parasite has potential for disease control

title_detail.value: New mobile element found in mosquito parasite has potential for disease control

summary: An interdisciplinary team of scientists has identified a new mobile DNA element in the Wolbachia parasite, which may contribute to improved control strategies for mosquito vectors of diseases such as Dengue and West Nile virus.
